ke":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-16T15:54:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>有冇人明griffen goods既原理<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nIncome effect &gt; substitution effect</blockquote><br />\nNegative income effect &gt; substitution effect<br />\n<br />\nWhen price increase, quantity demanded increase"},{"pid":"295f288d97285cf9123fc79244c00d1021af3424","tid":203087,"uid":43941,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-16T20:46:27.000Z","msg":"MV=PQ"},{"pid":"7b8dc3ff85952ab94d1e4c82901bc4c37a7b2b3d","tid":203087,"uid":36383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-16T21:00:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有冇人明griffen goods既原理<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nIncome effect &gt; substitution effect, inferior good 嘅一種。Demand curve 就向上斜，slope &gt; 0，因為Price decreases， substitution effect (Qd升)細過income effect(Qd)跌。<br />\n<br />\n做一次 Slutsky decomposition就係上面講堆野。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e04cb1ff01b5d8834d6e2d4a3451fdf61ae1db4","tid":203087,"uid":83016,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-16T21:32:23.000Z","msg":"loss averson"}]}